## Summary
This documentation describes Amplitude Data's Facebook Ads source integration that imports campaign-level ad spend, click, and impression data as Daily Ad Metrics events with properties like ad_metrics.impressions, ad_metrics.clicks, ad_group_id, and campaign_id for marketing analytics and CAC/ROAS calculations.

